\v 12 Isibili ngizakubuthanisa, Jakobe, wena wonke\x + 4.6.\x*; isibili\x + 4.6.\x* ngizaqoqa\x + Jer. 31.10.\x* insali yakoIsrayeli\x + 4.7.\x*; ngizababeka ndawonye njengezimvu zeBhozira\x + 1 Lan. 1.44.\x*, njengomhlambi phakathi\x + Jer. 31.10.\x* kwedlelo lawo\x + Isa. 5.17.\x*; bazabanga umsindo ngenxa \add yobunengi\x + Hez. 34.31; 36.37,38.\x*\add* babantu\x + Hez. 34.31; 36.37,38.\x*.
\v 13 Umfohli ukhuphukile phambi kwabo\x + Hlab. 107.16; Seb. 2.24.\x*; bafohlile, bedlula esangweni, baphuma ngalo. Njalo inkosi yabo izadlula phambi kwabo\x + 4.7; Hos. 3.5.\x*, leN\nd kosi\nd* esihlokweni sabo\x + Isa. 52.12.\x*.